OL,6,FA paedophile pub landlord who abused
OL,7,Fand raped multiple children has been
OL,8,Fjailed for 25 years.
OL,10,FPolice started an investigation into
OL,11,FRoy Borrowdale in 2018 after a victim
OL,12,Fcame forward to report abuse dating
OL,13,Fback to the early 2010s.
OL,15,FOfficers found incriminating evidence
OL,16,Fon a phone belonging to Borrowdale,
OL,17,Fwhich he said had been used by someone
OL,18,Felse in the pub.
OL,20,FThe first victim's testimony led to
OL,21,Fothers coming forward to report abuse.
