OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FFollowing a trial at Grimsby Crown
OL,7,FCourt, the 67-year-old, of Church
OL,8,FLane, Driffield, East Yorkshire, was
OL,9,Ffound guilty of eight counts of sexual
OL,10,Fabuse, including rape and sexual
OL,11,Fassault of girls under 16.
OL,13,FHe was cleared of raping a woman aged
OL,14,F16 or over.
OL,16,FHe was jailed for 25 years, with an
OL,17,Fadditional 12 months on licence.
OL,19,FOne victim told the court Borrowdale
OL,20,F"waited until I was vulnerable to
OL,21,Fstrip me of my dignity".
